193
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,160
Sepuluh kali.

194
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:56,359
Kemudian, setiap pagi...

195
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:11,640
Selamat malam.

196
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:12,880
Jiashang.

197
00:19:13,599 --> 00:19:14,319
Selamat malam.

